## Q3 Recommendation: Retroactive Fill → Smart Auto-Backfill

### The Flow

```
Day 1:  Campaign A starts running on Google Ads
Day 1-29: Hourly syncs create UNATTRIBUTED transactions (refLink=null, project=null)
Day 30: User maps Campaign A → binance.com/?ref=ducba → Project Binance
        ↓
        System auto-backfills: updates Day 1-29 UNATTRIBUTED transactions
        to point to the new mapping
```

### Rules

| Scenario | Behavior |
|----------|----------|
| Transactions exist as UNATTRIBUTED | **Re-attribute** them to the new mapping |
| Transactions exist under a DIFFERENT project | **Don't touch** — they belong to the old project |
| No transactions exist (campaign ran before our system started syncing) | **Pull from Google Ads API** → create BACKFILL transactions |

### Transaction Types

```typescript
type TransactionType =
  | "SYNC"          // normal hourly sync
  | "BACKFILL"      // historical data pulled on first mapping
  | "ADJUSTMENT"    // Google Ads correction (see Q7)
  | "REMAP"         // re-attribution from one project to another
```

### Backfill Example

```
Before mapping (Day 1-29 transactions exist as UNATTRIBUTED):

MICACE0001 | Day 1, 19:00  | null    | null    | Camp A | $200 | SYNC
MICACE0002 | Day 1, 20:00  | null    | null    | Camp A | $180 | SYNC
...
MICACE0028 | Day 29, 23:00 | null    | null    | Camp A | $210 | SYNC

After user maps on Day 30 → system backfills:

MICACE0001 | Day 1, 19:00  | ref=ducba | Binance | Camp A | $200 | SYNC → BACKFILL
MICACE0002 | Day 1, 20:00  | ref=ducba | Binance | Camp A | $180 | SYNC → BACKFILL
...
MICACE0028 | Day 29, 23:00 | ref=ducba | Binance | Camp A | $210 | SYNC → BACKFILL
MICACE0029 | Day 30, 00:00 | ref=ducba | Binance | Camp A | $190 | SYNC  ← normal from here
```

### Edge: What if Campaign A ran BEFORE our system existed?

Google Ads Reporting API provides historical data (up to ~2 years). On first mapping:

1. System pulls daily reports from Google Ads for available history
2. Creates BACKFILL transactions (1 per day — hourly not available for historical data)
3. All backfilled to the CURRENT mapping

```
MICACE-BF-001 | Day 1  | ref=ducba | Binance | Camp A | $4,800 | BACKFILL (daily)
MICACE-BF-002 | Day 2  | ref=ducba | Binance | Camp A | $5,100 | BACKFILL (daily)
...
MICACE-BF-029 | Day 29 | ref=ducba | Binance | Camp A | $4,500 | BACKFILL (daily)
MICACE0029    | Day 30 | ref=ducba | Binance | Camp A | $4,900 | SYNC (hourly from here)
```

> **Note:** BACKFILL transactions are daily granularity (Google Ads limitation for historical). 
> From mapping date forward, transactions are hourly (from live sync).

