## Complete Transaction Schema

```typescript
interface AdsTransaction {
  id: string;                    // "MICACE0001"
  timestamp: string;             // "2026-01-15T19:00:00Z"
  type: TransactionType;         // SYNC | BACKFILL | ADJUSTMENT | REMAP

  // ── Source ──
  campaignId: string;            // "camp-bn-search-1"
  campaignName: string;          // "Binance Sale - Search" (snapshot)
  accountId: string;             // "ads-001"

  // ── Destination (null if UNATTRIBUTED) ──
  refLinkId: string | null;      // "lr-binance-sale"
  refLinkUrl: string | null;     // "binance.com/?ref=ducba" (snapshot)
  projectId: string | null;      // "proj-binance"
  projectName: string | null;    // "Binance" (snapshot)

  // ── Amounts ──
  cost: number;                  // VND (can be negative for ADJUSTMENT)
  clicks: number;                // can be negative for ADJUSTMENT
  impressions: number;
  conversions: number;

  // ── Metadata ──
  adjustsTransactionId?: string; // for ADJUSTMENT: which original tx
  note?: string;                 // "Campaign đổi link ref + project"
  syncBatchId?: string;          // groups all tx from same sync cycle
}
```

## Hourly Sync Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A["⏰ Hourly Cron Job"] --> B["Pull Google Ads data<br/>(last 1 hour + corrections for last 7 days)"]
    B --> C{For each campaign}
    C --> D{Is campaign<br/>mapped to a<br/>project?}
    D -->|Yes| E["Create SYNC transaction<br/>refLink=X, project=Y, cost=$200"]
    D -->|No| F["Create SYNC transaction<br/>refLink=null, project=null<br/>(UNATTRIBUTED)"]
    C --> G{Check corrections<br/>for past 7 days}
    G --> H{Delta between<br/>Google Ads vs<br/>our SUM?}
    H -->|Yes| I["Create ADJUSTMENT transaction<br/>with delta amount"]
    H -->|No| J["No action"]
```

