## KPI Derivation

All metrics are derived from the transaction table:

```sql
-- Project Binance, Date range: Jan 1 to Jan 31

-- Total ads cost
SELECT SUM(cost) FROM transactions
WHERE projectId = 'proj-binance'
  AND timestamp BETWEEN '2026-01-01' AND '2026-01-31'
  AND type IN ('SYNC', 'BACKFILL', 'ADJUSTMENT')

-- Cost per ref (cross-metric)
WITH ads AS (
  SELECT SUM(cost) as total_cost FROM transactions
  WHERE projectId = 'proj-binance' AND ...
),
refs AS (
  SELECT SUM(count) as total_refs FROM ref_counts
  WHERE linkRefId IN (SELECT id FROM link_refs WHERE projectId = 'proj-binance')
    AND date BETWEEN '2026-01-01' AND '2026-01-31'
)
SELECT ads.total_cost / NULLIF(refs.total_refs, 0) AS cost_per_ref
```

